{"tid":432654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開房後不忿遭避開遂虛報強姦 美容師被情慾短訊出賣今認罪","createTime":"2017-10-11T16:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T02:56:28.000Z","uid":29627,"like":151,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0e110273b89c571dfb8befac4df354efdb6b1e","tid":432654,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171011/large/1507701918_4371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F1507701918_4371.jpg&h=17fbd1ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告鍾家怡(右)<br />\n<br />\n 30歲美容師今年8月中旬在街頭遇上陌生男子搭訕，對方主動索取她的手機號碼後約她外出，美容師認為兩人可成為情侶，遂於同月28日與對方到酒店開房，惟及後對方以需返回加拿大為由避開她，更在whatsApp封鎖她。美容師為報復而虛報遭對方強姦，令男方一度被捕。<br />\n<br />\n美容師鍾家怡今在裁判法院承認虛報有人犯罪，辯方求情指被告遭事主封鎖後曾上網找事主，發現他與不同女性有接觸及有關係，一時無知而犯案。裁判官鑑於被告原沒案底，一時衝動才犯案，現索取其社會服務令報告，准她保釋至本月25日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n控方案情指被告於8月31日到尖沙嘴警署報案稱被強姦，警方一度拘捕男事主，但翻查酒店閉路電視片段發現兩人進出酒店時均手拖手及接吻，警員檢查被告手機更發現被告與男方的情慾短訊，被告終改口承認報假案。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171011/57318023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171011%2F57318023&d=CkoTydT07GA4d35S6NBSJP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f07c5d32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171011%2F57318023&h=25872746\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171011/57318023</a>"},{"pid":"9009a422abb96a2b1ff41252c18338f5c54a6711","tid":432654,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658cfd70304e94bd6fd3ba02995da015c97902e4","tid":432654,"uid":64476,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"edc6b8537b150ba3dc8b34b670f3d2295bd7ef7a","tid":432654,"uid":389,